responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "FE1DAF1C4BBCAC836021DAAA9762DCA7", "Raucous as they are, the cries of the stricken blackbirds are like music to these ears. Let them fall, and blind the eyes of the goblin seers with them. It is well that you\'ve done that.It is time,however, that you left this range, godling. The Flame can tolerate your presence in our range no longer. In trade for your efforts toward our mutual enemies, I will grant you one more tale of the Ashen Flame, that you may take back to your peoples. The path will take you far from here, but you may learn much from it.")
name: SQ_RVR_0036_Hrok_50
